Package: dismapr
Title: NOAA's Distribution Mapping and Analysis Portal (DisMAP) data retrieval
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Ben", "Best", , "ben@ecoquants.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Melissa", "Karp", , "melissa.karp@noaa.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: DisMapR is an R package that provides functions to easily interact with NOAA's Distribution Mapping and Analysis Portal (DisMAP) APIs. This package allows users to: 1) Download species indicators data (Center of Gravity, depth metrics, etc.); 2) Access and download interpolated biomass raster layers; 3) Retrieve survey location points; 4) Create visualizations of species distributions.
